---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;">
        About us
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 items-center mb-20">
      <div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
          <strong>PENN USA Inc.</strong> is a 501(c)(3) Non-Profit, Tax Exempt Organization 
          registered in the State of Illinois. This organization was found in 
          2017 by a group of women from Chicagoland area to organize 
          and support women empowerment activities.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Our mission is to preserve and promote Tamil culture while empowering women 
          through education, cultural programs, and community support initiatives. 
          We believe in creating a strong network of Tamil women who can support 
          each other in their personal and professional growth.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pink-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pink-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Cultural Preservation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Maintaining Tamil traditions and heritage</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pink-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pink-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Women Empowerment</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Supporting women's growth and leadership</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pink-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pink-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Community Building</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Creating strong bonds within our community</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-pink-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-pink-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Educational Support</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Promoting learning and skill development</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors">
            read more
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-0">
        <img 
          src="/images/gallery/home-abt-img-2019.jpg" 
          alt="Community members working together"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full h-96 object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Penn Pledge Section -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-50 to-rose-50 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;">
          Penn Pledge (Penn Urudhi Mozhi)
        </h3>
      </div>
      
      <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3 lg:gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 mb-8 lg:mb-0">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-100 to-orange-200 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <img 
              src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4207707/pexels-photo-4207707.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400" 
              alt="Tamil Scroll"
              class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
            />
            <div class="text-center">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">பெண் உறுதி மொழி</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Tamil written in English</h4>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <p><em>Thannikarattra thani peraatral udaiyavalaai</em></p>
              <p><em>Thinniya mana mei ngaanam kondavalaai</em></p>
              <p><em>Manniya nilai nilai konda maanpumigalai</em></p>
              <p><em>Penniya perumai nilai konda pengalai</em></p>
              <p><em>Nanniya nilai nilai konda naangal</em></p>
              <p><em>Enniya nilai nilai konda engalai</em></p>
              <p><em>Penniya perumai nilai konda pengalai</em></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">English Translation</h4>
            <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
              <p>I am inimitable & unique in potential</p>
              <p>I am strong willed and prudent</p>
              <p>I am a woman of honor and dignity</p>
              <p>I am a woman of pride and prestige</p>
              <p>We are women of good values</p>
              <p>We are women of noble thoughts</p>
              <p>We are women of pride and prestige</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>